data.description: Located in the gated community of Boca Royale, this move-in ready, open concept home, boasts of 3 bedrooms, great room with den and dining area, and 2 ½ baths, with stunning wide lake views. The Great Room is the center of attention in this open concept, split floor plan, with sliding glass doors, coffered ceilings, and finished with crown molding. The upgraded gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, an Oversized island, stainless steel appliances, and a butler's pantry, is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy your morning coffee, afternoon breeze or evening sunset from the oversized screened lanai, which overlooks the serene lake. A 1,000-acre gated community of custom-designed Tuscan, Mediterranean and French Colonial homes, Boca Royale features beautifully landscaped streets, lakes, and nature preserves, an 18-hole par 72 semi-private golf course, tennis and pickleball courts, a fitness center, a dog park and a clubhouse with a full- service restaurant. You will be just minutes away from Manasota Key and Boca Grande where you can enjoy pristine Gulf beaches unique local cuisine and world-class fishing. Landscape maintenance and a Boca Royale social membership are included in the HOA fees. Golf membership is optional.
